<H1>Concepts&nbsp;Review</H1>
<p><font face="Verdana" size="5">Object Context</font><font size="5">:</font><font face="Verdana" size="5"> 
Each context is represented as an Object called an Object Context</font></p>
<p><font face="Verdana" size="5">Call Context: Similar to contexts being 
represented as objects</font></p>
<p><font face="Verdana" size="5">Causalities are 
represented as Call Context objects</font></p>
<p><font size="5">Object context: model the space an object lives in</font></p>
<p><font size="5">Call context: model work being done in that space </font></p>
